// one line comments:
    start with "//" and end with "\n"
    can contain any characters after "//" and before "/n".
    lasts exactly 1 line

    1) start with "//" and end with "\n". can contain any characters after "//" and before "/n".
    // @@@;;;
    --> good
    // public static void
    --> good

    2) lasts exactly 1 line
    public // valid comment
    main --> good
    public // not a
    valid comment
    main --> bad
